{"tid":479473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［藏獨？不了!］達賴喇嘛：我們西藏希望留在中國","createTime":"2017-11-25T07:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T07:16:45.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d704268678dd84e3989e62496439e3efee8793f4","tid":479473,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"西藏流亡精神領袖達賴喇嘛，周四（23日）在印度加爾各答商會舉行的研討會，回答提問時，評論中國與西藏的關係時，表示西藏並非尋求脫離中國獨立，「我們希望留在中國，我們希望有更多發展」。 <br />\n<br />\n達賴喇嘛表示，雖然中國和西藏有些「爭鬥」，但兩國關係密切，又強調︰「過去的就過去了。我們必須着眼於未來」。他還澄清，西藏人民並不反對中國，希望跟中國在一起。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171124/mobile/bkncn-20171124232000778-1124_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171124%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171124232000778-1124_05011_001.html&d=N8XfqDuzeZiIqZa3Yt1pi7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=addda378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171124/mobile/bkncn-20171124232000778-1124_05011_001.html</a><br />\n達賴都變五毛"},{"pid":"2dab37ffd4b8177c7211f1e0dbf537ff7c27528d","tid":479473,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2239d72577bdedfe06e102974c637a1a1383fecd","tid":479473,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"人大了就會愛國原來係真"},{"pid":"a9abdf8e683a325d73bc01506963562571331b5c","tid":479473,"uid":59840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩國</span></strong>關係密切"}]}